Package spold2

Class Spold2

java.lang.Object
spold2.Spold2
public class Spold2 extends Object
A utility class for working with EcoSpold 2 data sets. Basically, there are two types of methods in this class: (1) the get-methods return the property from the document (2) the other methods create the property and all the intermediate data structures if it does not yet exist.
